							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="Speech"><a name="time_20160922 15:40:26" ></a><strong>PEENI HENARE (Labour—</strong><strong>Tāmaki</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Makaurau</strong><strong>)</strong>: </p><p class="IndentMarginalone">[Authorised Te Reo text to be inserted by the Hansard Office.]</p><p class="IndentMarginalone">[Authorised translation to be inserted by the Hansard Office.]</p></div></body>
